{"tid":908411,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人有恐男症or恐女症？","createTime":"2018-11-19T14:19:19.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-20T10:35:29.000Z","uid":36366,"like":6,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"5558d6f0468bd29220c2607809f25906dc07d55c","tid":908411,"uid":36366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T14:19:19.000Z","msg":"利申 本人自細讀男女校<br />\n覺得同同性傾偈都唔係好交到心<br />\n對異性更加係恐懼<br />\n睇太多新聞，上太多高登連登，覺得啲靚又好唔靚都好，同你傾偈嘅異性就係有企圖<br />\n出嚟搵工又比啲好smart 嘅人呃過（利申本人肥毒柒），所以對呢類人係極度恐懼<br />\n有冇人有啲咁嘅經歷而家又正常返？"},{"pid":"714e9ad9760e46ec442b872320ad4b4abdbeb72b","tid":908411,"uid":36366,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T14:32:07.000Z","msg":"自己平時喺網上都有識啲異性朋友，都好傾得計<br />\n但一去到現實就完全係恐懼<br />\n唔知係咪對自己太無自信<br />\n但兩登名句又話毒撚最忌有自信<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b6460bc2e32d02750d0a92155cf6067212fb726","tid":908411,"uid":36366,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T14:42:55.000Z","msg":"毒撚開post無人理<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54cd0f6ce6c79b93ce6fc87cf16eca1767a8de52","tid":908411,"uid":36366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T15:56:50.000Z","msg":"點解要比負皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7dfb543c89a95b36d6546531ce3c8447f5387c6","tid":908411,"uid":35382,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T15:58:02.000Z","msg":"因為月薪一萬元<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2f15397df174ee5299cb125aeeb770e9744ea55","tid":908411,"uid":28624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T15:59:37.000Z","msg":"社交恐懼？"},{"pid":"cb96620b85595c163bb3d3a1ebea53de1b775e08","tid":908411,"uid":36366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a7dfb543c89a95b36d6546531ce3c8447f5387c6","tid":908411,"uid":35382,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score